{"title":"Moots Offers Trade-Up Program","link":"https://theradavist.com/moots-offers-trade-up-program/","date":1715870646000,"content":"<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1333\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/Moots_Trade-up-program-zerkel.jpeg?fit=1200,1333&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/Moots_Trade-up-program-zerkel.jpeg?w=2000&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/Moots_Trade-up-program-zerkel.jpeg?resize=1200,800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/Moots_Trade-up-program-zerkel.jpeg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/Moots_Trade-up-program-zerkel.jpeg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /></p>\n<p>Got an old Moots like the <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/jah-blessed-1989-moots-zerkel-mtb/\" target=\"_blank\">1989 Zerkel shown above</a>, or perhaps you have a <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/cerro-gordo-excursion-disconnecting-with-a-sram-axs-equipped-moots-baxter/\" target=\"_blank\">Baxter</a>, and you’re looking for a new bike like a <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/johns-moots-womble-29er-loaded-for-the-san-juan-hut-telluride-to-moab-route/\" target=\"_blank\">Womble</a> or a <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/moots-routt-esc-review/\" target=\"_blank\">Routt ESC</a>? Well, Moots just announced an all-<a href=\"https://moots.com/blog/new-bike-day-moots-trade-up-program\" target=\"_blank\">new trade-up program</a>. There’s no doubt that many of the beloved products the brand has produced since 1981 still make riders smile, 20 and 30 years later.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1333\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2014/09/1989_Moots_Zerkel-17.jpg?fit=1200,1333&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2014/09/1989_Moots_Zerkel-17.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2014/09/1989_Moots_Zerkel-17.jpg?resize=1200,799&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2014/09/1989_Moots_Zerkel-17.jpg?resize=1900,1266&amp;quality=75 1900w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2014/09/1989_Moots_Zerkel-17.jpg?resize=1335,889&amp;quality=75 1335w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2014/09/1989_Moots_Zerkel-17.jpg?resize=700,466&amp;quality=75 700w\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1333\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2014/09/1989_Moots_Zerkel-27.jpg?fit=1200,1333&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2014/09/1989_Moots_Zerkel-27.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2014/09/1989_Moots_Zerkel-27.jpg?resize=1200,799&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2014/09/1989_Moots_Zerkel-27.jpg?resize=1900,1266&amp;quality=75 1900w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2014/09/1989_Moots_Zerkel-27.jpg?resize=1335,889&amp;quality=75 1335w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2014/09/1989_Moots_Zerkel-27.jpg?resize=700,466&amp;quality=75 700w\" /></p>\n<p>Moots owners now have the opportunity to turn their existing, rideable frame, into a $2,000 credit towards a complete bike direct from Moots! This program applies whether you’re the original owner or not. There are no model or production year restrictions. Check out more at <a href=\"https://moots.com/blog/new-bike-day-moots-trade-up-program\" target=\"_blank\">Moots</a>.</p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/moots-offers-trade-up-program/\">Moots Offers Trade-Up Program</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://theradavist.com\">The Radavist</a>.</p>","author":"John Watson","siteTitle":"The Radavist","siteHash":"96eb481d8084f04a4602bac57874ba717baf56b758f45547b5caf2312da766ef","entryHash":"c360ddcc2c07320b84311881e22dca59f99c98f44e9f1182a7cabaa4045a77bb","category":"Cycling"}